*Veza* je između njih dvoje postala još jača. (The connection between them became even stronger.)

Ona se veoma lako povezuje sa ljudima. (She gets easily connected with people.)

Ova *veza* će biti najjača karika u lancu. (This link will be the strongest link in the chain.)

On je napravio novu *vezu* sa starim prijateljem. (He made a new connection with an old friend.)

Ona nije uspela da začara *vezu* između njih. (She was not able to cast a spell on the bond between them.)